<p><span style="font-size: 13.008px;"><a href="mailto:rjohnson@astro.as.utexas.edu">Rebecca Johnson</a>, Communications Mgr.</span><br /><span style="font-size: 13.008px;">McDonald Observatory</span><br /><span style="font-size: 13.008px;">The University of Texas at Austin</span><br /><span style="font-size: 13.008px;">512-475-6763</span></p>
