  <div class="content">
    <div class="image"><a href="https://www.nasa.gov/ames/kepler/briefing-materials-eighth-planet-circling-distant-star-discovered-using-artificial-intelligence"><img src="https://mcdonaldobservatory.org/sites/default/files/styles/7colcrop/public/images/news/releases/linked/Kepler90-VS-solarsystem.jpg?itok=wOBsSPK3" alt="K90vsSolarSystem" /></a></div>  </div>
